         Changing robes isn't nessesary especially if you're in lich form. A smart tank will use disc to kill your pet in a few seconds then dispel what he can of the dots and come attack you. A nice Vexing and Funeral Pyre and they're hurt if not dead... if you have channeling focus, channel a deflux or so if you're fighting a gimp melee but you can also take the time to add pyro or splurt then kite him around. Rogues i think are the hardest to duel... backstabs can be crippling, takes em 11 seconds to down spectre pet with disc, and poison sucks when it lands.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
